 subject to a set of triangle inequalities in the\nsuperspins. For completeness, we also analyse the structure of three-point\nfunctions involving conserved higher-spin supercurrents and scalar superfields.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 1 Feb 2023 17:05:13 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 5 Apr 2023 08:41:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-04"}
