. We conclude on the\nfeasibility of fabricating homogeneous thick GaP1-xNx layers lattice matched to\nSi (x = 0.021) or even with N content up to x=0.04. The possibility of\nexceeding a N mole fraction of 0.04 without inducing coupled\nmorphological-compositional modulations has also been demonstrated when the\nlayer thickness is kept below the critical value for the 2D-3D growth mode\ntransition.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 2 Feb 2023 15:08:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-02-03"}
