rption now\ndepends on the number of collisions $\\ell(t)$ of the RTP with the boundary.\nFinally, we extend the theory by taking absorption to depend on the individual\noccupation times at the two ends.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 2 Feb 2023 15:24:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-10"}
